attachments.title: Plum Raises $9 Million Series A Led By Khosla Ventures
attachments.text: Plum, the first appliance that automatically preserves, chills and serves wine by the glass, raises $9 million Series A led by Khosla Ventures to transform wine by the glass at home and luxury hotels.
